revision.text:
'''[[Belarusian Cup]] 2000–01''' was the tenth season of the [[Belarus]]ian annual [[football (soccer)|football]] cup competition. Contrary to the league season, it is conducted in a fall-spring rhythm. The first games were played on June 14, 2000.

==First round==
The games were played on 14 June 2000.

