inal) in {{flagicon|CZE}} [[Špindlerův Mlýn]] ** Men's Slopestyle winner: {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Jamie Nicholls (snowboarder)|Jamie Nicholls]] ** Women's Slopestyle winner: {{flagicon|GER}} [[Silvia Mittermueller]]
