{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2014}} {{Unreferenced|date= November 2014}} {{Infobox stadium | stadium_name = Gradski Stadion | nickname = | image = | fullname = | location = [[Laktaši]], [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]] | coordinates = | broke_ground = | built = | opened = | renovated = | expanded = | closed = | demolished = | owner = [[FK Laktaši]] | operator = [[FK Laktaši]] | surface = | construction_cost = | architect = | structural engineer = | services engineer = | general_contractor= | project_manager = | main_contractors = | former_names = | tenants = [[FK Laktaši]] | seating_capacity = 5,000 | dimensions = }}
'''Gradski Stadion''' is a football [[stadium]] in [[Laktaši]], [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]]. It is the home stadium of [[FK Laktaši]] of the [[Premier League of Bosnia and Herzegovina]]. The stadium holds 5,000 spectators.
