'''Karketu Dili''' is a football club of [[East Timor]] based in [[Dili]].<ref>[http://www.national-football-teams.com/club/19929/2016/Karketu_Dili.html Profile on NFT]</ref> The team plays in the [[Liga Futebol Amadora]]. They finished runner-up in the [[2016 Liga Futebol Amadora]] after only lost productivity goals than the league champions [[Sport Laulara e Benfica|Benfica Laulara]].

